description: A top member of a party hostile to LGBT rights is said to have attended a "gay sex party" in Brussels.
title: Jozsef Szajer: Hungary MEP quits after allegedly fleeing gay orgy
title_page: Jozsef Szajer: Hungary MEP quits after allegedly fleeing gay orgy - BBC News
maintext: "Narcotics were found in his backpack," a statement by prosecutors says. "The man was unable to produce any identity documents. He was escorted to his place of residence where he identified himself as S. J. (1961) by means of a diplomatic passport."
